Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
all_outputs(25.10)                                          all_outputs(25.10)

Name
       all_outputs  -  Creates a collection of all output ports in the current
       design

Syntax
       all_outputs

       [-help]

       [-clock <list_of_clocks>]

       [-edge_triggered]

       [-level_sensitive]

       Creates a collection of all output ports in the current design. You can
       limit the contents of a collection to ports with output delay  relative
       to  a  specific clock. You can assign these ports to a variable or pass
       them using another command.

Parameters
       -help  Prints the command usage.

       -clock <list_of_clocks>
              Considers only output ports with an output delay relative  to  a
              specific collection or a list of clocks.

       -edge_triggered
              Returns  a  collection of output ports with the set_output_delay
              -clock constraint.

       -level_sensitive
              Returns a collection of output ports with  the  set_output_delay
              -level_sensitive constraint.

Example
              *

                The  following  command  returns  a collection of output ports
                with an output delay relative to ideal_clk:

                > all_outputs -clock ideal_clk

Related Information
              * get_ports

              * report_ports

              * set_output_delay

